### ==========================================================
### Wyze API Reference
### ==========================================================
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Run: ./api/gen-env.sh secrets/secrets.yaml .env
###   2. Run requests top-to-bottom (login first, others use token)
### ==========================================================

### Variables
@authHost = https://auth-prod.api.wyze.com
@apiHost = https://api.wyzecam.com
@email = {{$dotenv WYZE_EMAIL}}
@passwordMd5 = {{$dotenv WYZE_PASSWORD_MD5}}
@keyId = {{$dotenv WYZE_KEY_ID}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv WYZE_API_KEY}}

### ----- Authentication -----

### Login — get access_token and refresh_token
### Docs: https://support.wyze.com/hc/en-us/articles/16129834216731
### Rate limited — do NOT call repeatedly, use refresh endpoint instead
# @name login
POST {{authHost}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json
keyid: {{keyId}}
apikey: {{apiKey}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{passwordMd5}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.access_token}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.refresh_token}}

### Refresh access token — use this instead of re-logging in
### Access token valid: 2 days | Refresh token valid: 30 days
# @name refresh
POST {{apiHost}}/app/user/refresh_token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "app_ver": "wyze_developer_api",
  "app_version": "wyze_developer_api",
  "phone_id": "wyze_developer_api",
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}",
  "sc": "wyze_developer_api",
  "sv": "wyze_developer_api",
  "ts": {{$timestamp}}000
}

### ----- Devices -----

### List all devices
# @name devices
POST {{apiHost}}/app/v2/home_page/get_object_list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "access_token": "{{accessToken}}",
  "phone_id": "wyze_developer_api",
  "app_ver": "wyze_developer_api",
  "app_version": "wyze_developer_api",
  "sc": "wyze_developer_api",
  "sv": "wyze_developer_api",
  "ts": {{$timestamp}}000
}

### Get device property list
### Use to read device-specific properties (e.g., garage door state)
### Key properties for Garage Door Controller (HL_CGDC):
###   P1301 — open_close_state: 0=closed, 1=open
###   P1056 — accessory_state: 0=closed (app), 1=open, 2=closed (automation)
# @name properties
POST {{apiHost}}/app/v2/device/get_property_list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "access_token": "{{accessToken}}",
  "phone_id": "wyze_developer_api",
  "app_ver": "wyze_developer_api",
  "app_version": "wyze_developer_api",
  "sc": "wyze_developer_api",
  "sv": "wyze_developer_api",
  "ts": {{$timestamp}}000,
  "device_mac": "{{$dotenv GARAGE_CAM_MAC}}",
  "device_model": "{{$dotenv GARAGE_CAM_MODEL}}"
}
